title: Barter / Trading System
body: A barter system where one can propose a trade of in-game assets for another users in-game assets. Very similar to making someone an offer in tokens but with in-game assets instead. The recipient can decline or accept the offer. If accepted, users execute a trade. There is no limit of the amount of items that can be traded for another.
